  "cscw_dialogue": [
    {
      "turn_id": 1,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "我们需要梳理一下页面发布的完整生命周期。目前团队在Drafting、Scheduling和Published这三个阶段的操作有些混乱，特别是published_at这个字段的状态流转。我想用时间线图来可视化这个过程。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Page Publish Lifecycle",
        "Drafting",
        "Scheduling",
        "Published",
        "published_at"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 2,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "明白。我注意到你提到了三个阶段，那在Drafting阶段，published_at初始状态应该是nil对吗？另外我看到系统里有IoT_Industrial_TelemetryStream这个模块，它在这个流程里扮演什么角色？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Drafting",
        "published_at",
        "IoT_Industrial_TelemetryStream"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 3,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "对的，初始状态published_at是nil。IoT_Industrial_TelemetryStream是我们的工业遥测数据流，在创建页面时会关联这个标识。另外Drafting阶段还需要体现通过content_page_blocks来添加内容块的操作。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "published_at",
        "IoT_Industrial_TelemetryStream",
        "content_page_blocks",
        "Create page",
        "Add content blocks"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 4,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "好的，我把Drafting阶段画好了：创建页面时published_at为nil并关联IoT_Industrial_TelemetryStream，以及通过content_page_blocks添加内容块。接下来Scheduling阶段，是不是设置published_at为当前时间就算进入定时发布状态了？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Drafting",
        "Scheduling",
        "published_at",
        "Set published_at now",
        "scheduled"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 5,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "是的，设置published_at为now就变成scheduled状态。同时这个阶段还要更新privacy、layout、slug这些字段，而且缓存键要包含updated_at。我觉得这个细节很重要，得体现出来。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Scheduling",
        "published_at",
        "privacy",
        "layout",
        "slug",
        "updated_at",
        "cached keys"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 6,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "已添加Scheduling阶段的两个节点。现在来看Published阶段，逻辑应该是published_at小于等于当前时间就正式发布，但可见性还要受权限策略控制对吧？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Published",
        "published_at <= now",
        "Visible if policy allows"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 7,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "没错，published_at <= now是published状态。但可见性逻辑要拆清楚：privacy为public时直接可见，或者用户有authorized权限时也能看到。不要写成简单的\"公开可见\"，要保留策略判断的语义。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Published",
        "published_at <= now",
        "Visible if policy allows",
        "privacy public",
        "authorized"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 8,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "理解了，Published阶段我拆成两个节点：一个是published_at <= now的状态判定，另一个是Visible if policy allows的可见性规则，具体区分privacy public和authorized两种情况。整个时间线图完成了，你看是否符合预期？",
